ApplicableFor ExportFFmpegOptions::apptable [static]

Some controls (parameters they represent) are only applicable to a number of codecs and/or formats. Syntax: first, enable a control for each applicable format-codec combination then disable it for anything else "any" - any format CODEC_ID_NONE - any codec This list must end with {FALSE,FFmpegExportCtrlID(0),CODEC_ID_NONE,NULL}
